Hordeum vulgare
), leading to altered biomass allocation in neighbouring plants. Ann. Bot. 115, 961–970. https://doi.org/10.1093/aob/mcv036.

Stanys, V., Weckman, A., Staniene, G., Duchovskis, P., 2006. In vitro induction of polyploidy in Japanese quince (
